        "question": "Consider the following Assertion (A) and Reason (R) and choose your answer from the given code: Assertion (A): The upper surface of the wings of an aeroplane is made convex and the lower surface is made concave. Reason (R): The air current at the top has less velocity and thus less pressure at the bottom than at the top. Code:",
