        "chapterIndex": 18,
        "qNoInChapter": 110,
        "question": "Which of the following statements with reference to ‘blood’ is/are correct? 1. Blood is composed of plasma and different types of cells. 2. The presence of haemoglobin makes blood appear red. Select the correct answer from the code given below: Code:",
