        "id": 1113,
        "chapter": "Diseases and Treatment",
        "chapterIndex": 20,
        "qNoInChapter": 17,
        "question": "Consider the given statement and reason: Assertion: Smallpox is transmitted by a virus. Reason: The patient should rest on separate bed.",
